<Paragraph FontWeight="Bold" FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="16">
Features
</Paragraph>

<List Margin="25,0,0,0">

<ListItem><Paragraph>Chart series data points can be sorted using the <Bold>IsSortData</Bold> property.</Paragraph></ListItem>
</List>
<Paragraph FontWeight="Bold" FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="16">
Interactive Features
</Paragraph>

    <List Margin="25,0,0,0">
        
        <ListItem>
            <Paragraph>The chart type for both Indexed and non-indexed axis can be selected using the
                <Bold>Chart Type</Bold> combo box.</Paragraph>
        </ListItem>
        <ListItem>
            <Paragraph>Select the sorting direction as ascending or descending from the
                <Bold>Sort Direction</Bold> combo box.</Paragraph>
        </ListItem>
        <ListItem>
            <Paragraph>The sorting path for the Indexed Axis can be chosen as
                X-axis or XY-axis from the <Bold>Sorting path</Bold>.</Paragraph>
        </ListItem>
    </List>



